g.title: http://www.semanticweb.org/van_gogh_ontology#Saint-Rémy-de-Provence
g.text: Saint-Rémy-de-Provence is a commune in the
d'Azur, Southern France. Located in the northern
part of the Alpilles, of which it is the main
town, it had a population of 9,893 in 2017.

g.title: http://www.semanticweb.org/van_gogh_ontology#Arles
g.text: Arles is a coastal city and commune in the South
of France, a subprefecture in the Bouches-du-Rhône
